  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST OUR ANOTHER CARD BATTLER!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088770/extras/87b3e4523bac908038b66fdf90605265.poster.avif?t=1772786836\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088770/extras/87b3e4523bac908038b66fdf90605265.webm?t=1772786836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088770/extras/87b3e4523bac908038b66fdf90605265.mp4?t=1772786836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own hero, extract souls of your enemies and make cards out of them, break through tough battles, die, and go all over again...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Deck of Souls</strong>, you will:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your enemies' souls into your cards and mix different classes’ abilities to uncover your true power. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your hero’s capabilities and appearance, pick between several distinct classes, use the RPG elements and inventory system to your advantage, and take the proper outfit. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make choices and decide the bosses’ fate. Execute them for their sins or spare them, so that they will come to help.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088770/extras/87b3e4523bac908038b66fdf90605265.poster.avif?t=1772786836\" width=618 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088770/extras/87b3e4523bac908038b66fdf90605265.webm?t=1772786836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088770/extras/87b3e4523bac908038b66fdf90605265.mp4?t=1772786836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own hero, extract souls of your enemies and make cards out of them, break through tough battles, die, and go all over again...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Deck of Souls</strong>, you will:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your enemies' souls into your cards and mix different classes’ abilities to uncover your true power. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your hero’s capabilities and appearance, pick between several distinct classes, use the RPG elements and inventory system to your advantage, and take the proper outfit. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make choices and decide the bosses’ fate. Execute them for their sins or spare them, so that they will come to help.</p></li></ul>",
